_sText:
This is my new Gun-Game map!
                         Meant to be played on gun game servers!
there are spawn points opposite of each other with a building in the middle, the middle has glass which can be broken after 500 damage so you can shoot from 1 end to the other, the glass was added to prevent spawn killing. In the middle are 4 holes 2 are blue 2 are red drop down the red to get to the bottom and go up the blue to get to the top. on each side of the map there is a staircase to go up and down as well. have fun guys!

Many thanks to all who helped and tested with me, I appreciate the help very much and thank you all for your ideas. Without you guys this map wouldn't have been possible =)
